<div id="options">
    <div class="options-header">
        <h1>Why volunteer?</h1>
        <p>Volunteering in Pu Nagol offers a chance to address critical issues and make a real difference. By helping build and renovate schools, you can improve quality of education for kids. Food insecurity is another major problem, with many struggling to access nutritious meals. Join us in Pu Nagol and be part of the change that transforms lives and communities.</p>
    </div>
