            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="/img/volunteer-teach.jpg" alt="Convenience" class="card-img">
            <div class="card-text" id="card-text2">
                <h1>Teach</h1>
                <p>Do you have a passion for helping empovrished kids learn english and other life skills</p>
                <p>Click to find out more!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img src="/img/food-donate.jpg" alt="Bookings" class="card-img">
            <div class="card-text" id="card-text3">
                <h1>Food</h1>
